This repository provides a GtkSourveView language definition for the MAGMA
computational algebra system language.

Visit http://magma.maths.usyd.edu.au/magma/ for more information on MAGMA.

To use the language definition file it has to be installed. The instructions
below outline a means of installation.

1) create a ~/.local/share/gtksourceview-2.0/language-specs directory.
2) place magma.lang in above directory.
